{"tid":486572,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"食飯聽到一對男女都幾癲","createTime":"2017-12-02T03:54:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-02T04:22:47.000Z","uid":52585,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3a7b4fa3a86bc934fb62907b8388749db4531d84","tid":486572,"uid":52585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T03:54:39.000Z","msg":"是咁的<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我聽到隔離位講佢親戚朋友d野，大概都係結婚買樓女方嫌3嫌4點點點，講到幾句whatsapp係咁：<br />\n<br />\n女：4百幾尺好細呀，間房淨係放到一個衣櫃，點住呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n男：一係我俾晒個櫃你用啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n女：你俾晒我都唔夠用呀！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後女又話：有乜理由要我拉低自己生活質素同你住？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁個男就成隻狗咁俾個女狂鬧，又冇講d咩<br />\n<br />\n個女又有同其他人講嫌個男條件差，身高職業樣貌通通數齊，我仲聽到佢地話個女只為左有個伴，完全冇愛，只係男一廂情願<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽到我隔夜飯都嘔埋出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而根據佢地講，個男就係典型弱雞港男<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢對男女真係極品<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99e6d8dfd80aad92be4c893544f5ce599b4ca2ab","tid":486572,"uid":127272,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T03:55:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/02/115538_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F02%2F115538_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=b94237e1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4cdd4758fd62bb8a61dda14a11e7b64a96f12bc0","tid":486572,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T04:16:40.000Z","msg":"樓上做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b